<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. لِحِفْظِ نُصُوصِ الدِّينِ أَهْلُ تَنَاصِرِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِذَا مَا بَدَا نَصَّ الْكِتَابِ وَسُنَّةٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تَنَادَوا عِبَادَ اللهِ هَلْ مِنْ مُثَابِرِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَعَضُّوا عَلَيْهَا بِالنَّوَاجِذِ فَاهْتَدُوا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا رَغِبُوا عَنْهَا لِخِرْصِ الْخَوَاطِرِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>عَلَيْكَ بِهَاتَيْكَ الصِّفَاتِ مُنَافِساً<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَللهِ مَا أَسْنَا سَنَاهَا لِسَائِرِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>هُمْ الْقَوْمُ لا يَثْنِيهُمْ عَنْ مُرَادِهِمْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مَلامَةُ لُوَّامٍ وَخُذْلانُ نَاصِرِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بِنَفْسِي فَتَى مَا زَالَ يَدْأَبُ دَائِماً<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِلى رَبِّهِ أَكْرِمْ بِهِ مِنْ مُهَاجِرِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مُكِبّاً عَلَى أَيِ الْكِتَابِ وَدَرْسِهِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بِقَلْبٍ حَزِينٍ عِنْدَ تِلْكَ الزَّوَاجِرِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَيَا لَيْتَنِي أَلْقَاهُ يَوْماً لَعَلَّهُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يُخَبِّرُنِي عَمَّا حَوَى فِي الضَّمَائِرِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَنَرْفَعُ أَيْدِينَا إِلى اللهِ بِالدُّعَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لِيَنْصُرَ دِينَ الْمُصْطَفَى ذِيِ الْمَفَاخِرِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَيَنْصُرَ أَحْزَابَ الشَّرِيعَةِ وَالْهُدَى<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَيَقْمَعَ أَهْلَ الزَّيْغِ مِنْ كُلِّ فَاجِرِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَآهٍ عَلَى تَفْرِيقِ شَمْلٍ فَهَلْ لِمَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>مَضَى عَوْدَةٌ نَحْوَ السِّنِينِ الْغَوَابِرِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>